  <h1 id="title">Charles Thomas Munger</h1>
  <p>“Marches to the beat of his own music, and it’s music like virtually no one else is listening to.” <cite> Warren Buffett </cite></p>
  <figure id="img-div">
    <img
      id="image"
      src="https://images.app.goo.gl/H5pgRJsTYbRW4Bsx8"
